title: 2021 Maricopa County presidential ballot audit
deleted: Evidence presented shows many irregularities and security weaknesses in voting machine and software.

title: 2021 Maricopa County presidential ballot audit
added: Logan stated that his audit could not conclude if there was fraud in the mail in ballots, just that it was "highly suspicious".<ref name=Evoy/> Logan expressed reluctance to conduct further election audits in other states, attributing this to actions by right-wingers.<ref name=Gilbert/> Logan described receiving many messages criticizing him for "not doing enough", stating that he "did not put enough on the line".<ref name=Gilbert/>
